
System statistics scripts

1. Requirements
	- Ruby 1.8.6, 1.8.7
    - RRDTool >= 1.2.0 with Ruby bindings

2. Installation
Use the install.sh script for installation:

    ./install.rb

to change the install path use PREFIX=/path/to/sysstat:

   ./install.rb PREFIX=/path/to/sysstat

The script will create a RC/Init-script which can be copied
or linked to the proper directories.
